title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - December 7, 2021
itunes:title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - December 7, 2021
description:
Adam and Mark link up for updates on a few stories we've been following including the trials of Jussie Smollett & Ghislaine Maxwell and, give an update on the fallout from Alec Baldwin's recent interview.

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
